Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beach time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sensei and Yui-neesan are in charge of supervising and driving today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you have a lot of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to impose on your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an officer in the traffic safety department, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all there is to know about traffic law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He passed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to safety first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui-neesan goes wild once her hand's on the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'll have to sacrifice Kagami and Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost sight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, that's the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a one-way street!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect both of them to fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That car's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both have perfect braking and drifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's practically on top of the FDI!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's got better acceleration!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's practically touching the guard rail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The point of attack will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the five consecutive hairpin curves ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the brakes die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the ******* D-like driving!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get sick whenever I'm in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I brought medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't feel sick at all with you at the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to be talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we find a hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clear sky is perfect weather for a day at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting worried there yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put on my swimsuit before we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a child...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of someone wearing a school swimsuit at this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people have special needs, Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-How old is that swimsuit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing a swim ring when you're good at sports stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean doesn't exist solely for wasting effort on swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take it leisurely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leisure time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, to meet those special needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have to wear a school swimsuit with a swim ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People with special needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't be coming to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watermelon cracking is the usual event in manga and anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it doesn't happen much in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but people probably feel like it's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you blow up a watermelon with a gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll end up covered in watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You watch too much anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever played it before, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, on second thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like something rich people would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess your eyes don't end up like in manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But y'know, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girls only babysitting trip to the beach at this age...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're some lonely, single girls, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistak-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the alternative is resorting to bringing something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm all for a girls only trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're telling people to marry late these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well take our time and choose well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband just happens to be busy working far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already married!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is a Mecca for flirting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it doesn't apply to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's less annoying this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this thing probably makes people thing we're sisters here with our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a oopsie-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wazzup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of feels icky to sit down when I'm still wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can use an air chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My neck's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so happy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I got something straight out of a storybook beach house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how the curry is sauce and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is true beach house fare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, you wouldn't be willing to eat something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but here, it actually tastes good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beer they have at the beach is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generic beer isn't too bad once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it odd that they're charging 300 yen for a single frankfurter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're only half-cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll eat it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually like how their chicken is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dripping in grease and over-spiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this plain fried soba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is quite nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't stand eating this stuff at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata's touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this food really warrant so much praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough to make you run towards the ocean in a loincloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that another anime reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drank too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay another night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about work, Yui-neesan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also took tomorrow off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's freezing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a kidder, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is your hair all squeaky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after you've been in the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it has to do with salt or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main reason would be salt content and UV rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your hair always getting hit by UV rays?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason your hair is damaged by a trip to the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be the adhesion of salt from seawater and the sea breeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which absorbs the moisture from your hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which now suffers from exposure to strong UV rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you are exposed to strong UV rays outdoors...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your melanin levels will fade...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and your hair will become light brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if residual quantities of salt or chlorine remain in your hair, they may result in the discoloration of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual reason for hair damage in summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be UV rays and residual substances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The above factors cause damage to the cuticles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When exposed to strong UV rays...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the cysteine molecules found in strong hair are broken up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how other people would see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably sisters or cousins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui-neesan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the response I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut out the old geezer jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just triggered a flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the event starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to see both paths...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't forget to save often before a split!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No exceptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Picture complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you being like this is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why nobody came to hit on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're the one who brought it up in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could really care less about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kagami wanted someone to hit on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phooey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what you do about hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty smooth, so I don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, today was kinda dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine ended a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really sucks when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be sad if you were the only one who couldn't go in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But using that would be a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you think twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never used one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a candid conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, this is a true story...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo software wholesaler...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was on his way home from work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and got on the bus as usual late at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His house was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the end of the bus line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As more and more passengers got off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...eventually, he was the only person left on the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The driver thought that nobody was left on the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sang "DANZEN! Futari wa ***cure" at the top of his lungs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a rumor I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sukekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that mask from!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Inugami Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so much fun to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything funny to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl just took a step towards becoming an adult, Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.92,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comp Festival is a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause Japanese people are suckers for limited edition stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the words "limited edition" are enough to boost sales...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they could just add it to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would cheapen the value.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I went and asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean your room before break's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, flashback!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These textbooks are from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this album!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this picture of Dad a little risqué?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I started wondering about Dad's thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but are you getting any cleaning done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want these clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't need them, I'll take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll leave them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me I'm her trash can...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You end up looking through photo albums and stuff instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If any magazines are lying around, I start reading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. What about Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't throw anything away, so it takes a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's always slow to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, Kagami's always trigger happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is your impression of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so aggressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved your textbooks from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left them with my memories at my old school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, take them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're causing trouble for the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally finished cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that I'll never use this again, but then I remember how I just used it, so I can't throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There really are people who keep everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa seems the type.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like someone who even throws away useful stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as how you ditched your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go have your teeth taken care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before school starts up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I just don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would feel bad about forcing you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll have him come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A visit from the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already burst into the sixth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that you've all become familiar with this corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:18:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kogami Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that newbie Shiraishi-kun isn't used to the job and is a nervous wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.31,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.90,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.67,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to the mountains 'cause Akira-sama said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:13.67,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.85,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Went to the beach, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:18.70,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing everything I can to make this show funnier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:21.44,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The gum was hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.21,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What else will I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.35,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-four pieces in my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.05,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still worked hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:22.28,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was fifty-four pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all making his heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he gets used to the job soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he better watch how he talks to the veterans around here or else something may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hate that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we'll introduce a key Lucky Star character...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Konata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop blubbering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.10,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Konata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her hobbies are gaming, watching anime, and reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the data...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she always checks out new shows and books.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She games up a storm on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's a geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come up with something quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By geek, you mean that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who watch House Classics, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who watch A Dog of Flanders and cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which decade of geek are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing your homework!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get with the program!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess A Dog of Flanders had the whole cutesy, appealing character to soothe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people these days prefer a girl like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute as a button and pure as snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I look right, so do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I look left, so do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you line up for my concert the night before, you can't take a shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may cause hygienic problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you still want to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That determination burns as hot as the sun in wait of my arrival!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the bandanna around your head is drenched!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm doing handshakes afterward, they won't stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yapping away during MC without reading the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that just blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work hard for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How hard it is to be an idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've been through the good and bad, you'll see how it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do anything about the fans or clients you hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who Konata-san is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll see you on next week's Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even introduce Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like you introduced geeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the correspondent saw then was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kage sure is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you order a song, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-san's singing is quite refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can sing it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to sing, Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know many songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she went with this, huh?
