Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's the timing for ripping off a scab.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it starts to itch, and you're thinking that it's about time, so you pick it off bit by bit.
